<Layout title="Active Investor: Step 06 of The Stairway | Stairway Mortgage" description="Once you own one property, the question becomes: how do you scale? The Active Investor rung is about building a portfolio deliberately — using equity," canonical="https://stairwaymortgage.com/the-8-steps/active-investor/">
